---
title: Creamy Chicken & Bacon Filled Ravioli with Caramelized Shallots & Peas
description: Ravioli are one of our favorite pastas because they pack a punch—and these ones are packed with chicken AND bacon. That’s double the (meaty) trouble, double the fun. For the sauce, our chefs made a delicious cream elixir with peas and caramelized shallot. A squeeze of lemon on top adds a dash of zesty flavor to this creamy meal that comes together in just 15 minutes.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-chicken-bacon-mozzarella-ravioli-4b3b987b.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/creamy-chicken-bacon-filled-ravioli-617042e762e32739cb30d44c-7f21f747.pdf
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/creamy-chicken-bacon-filled-ravioli-617042e762e32739cb30d44c
cuisine: Italian
time required: 15 minutes
course: main course
author: HelloFresh
